text: Solid cup of sugarcane. The $4 jumbo is value for money. Big enough for 2.
Good cup of sugarcane, it’s not as sweet as what I’m used to which is great and pretty hard to find - the stall owners are friendly too 👍🏻

Very friendly and customer oriented aunty.  Juice was really fresh and nice. They are very confident of their Sugarcane Juice. When I wanted to pay, she told me, “Do not pay first. Try the drink first. If it’s not nice, you do not have to pay”.
My favorite sugarcane juice stand. Great quality sugarcane, not overpriced and the owner is the sweetest. 10/10 would recommend !
really self made juice. I tried the lime juice, all natural and yummy👍🏿👍🏿👍🏿 shiok
